DOCKER COMPOSE:
Docker compose is just a services within docker that let us launch multiple containers at the same time.

curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.10.0-rc2/dockercompose
   -$(uname -s) -$(uname -m)" -o /home/demo/docker-compose
chmod +x /home/demo/docker-compose
   


1. Create an yml file
    # docker-compose up
    # docker-compose down
    # docker-compose ps
    # docker-compose run project-name env
    # docker-compose stop
